│   │   └── <your_ai_app>/
│   ├── identity/                # Identity, KYC, reputation, SSO
│   │   └── <your_identity_app>/
│   ├── social/                  # Social, DAO, messaging, community
│   │   └── <your_social_app>/
│   ├── infrastructure/          # Oracles, bridges, wallets, tooling
│   │   └── <your_infra_app>/
